<h3 id='set_mugshot_texture_path'>: set_mugshot_texture_path()</h3><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight lua tab-lua"><code><span class="n">meta</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">set_mugshot_texture_path</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">_modpath</span><span class="o">..</span><span class="s2">"mugshot.png"</span> <span class="p">)</span>
